(53284, 61060, 3831, 11, '騰空少年', '寫給自己的一首畢業歌曲。', '2012-08-31 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 1, 7, '揚起一片土壤在你神經末梢 然後通過眉心直接尋找\r\n青色的天空在你的右眼 亞歷山大石是幸運的陪伴\r\n \r\n 踮起腳尖伸出聆聽的翅膀　感覺遠方的海風在宣揚\r\n在這個擁擠的世界上　還有一個地方無限的大\r\n \r\n踏出溫室的旅行是比較不確定\r\n隨身行李別忘了一路足夠的勇氣\r\n \r\n前進或稍作停留can not fall\r\n即使哪天它用盡你也不孤單\r\n \r\nnever never let you go\r\nnever never say hello\r\nnever never let me go\r\nnever never say goodbye', '', 444, '', '劉義棠', '劉義棠', '劉義棠', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-31 12:55:12', '2015-03-12 13:55:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53285, 61060, 3831, 4, '食月的人', '歌頌性愛的一首歌曲。', '2012-08-31 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 1, 7, '傳說有一種啃食著月亮的種族\r\n生長在一種安靜又潮濕的洞窟\r\n牠們進行著美麗又暴力的崇拜\r\n藉由彼此的身軀跳著奇怪的舞\r\n \r\n我們撕裂原始的美 在月光之間\r\n我們交織尺度性感的罪 在夜的草原\r\n \r\n思考在這時停止變成一隻豹\r\n性感冶豔的斑紋是你的外套\r\n本我的驅力進行 什麼都不用\r\n說我們不停瘋狂地纏繞 無可救藥', '', 374, '', '劉義棠', '劉義棠', '劉義棠', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-31 13:15:55', '2015-03-12 13:55:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53286, 25668, 0, 1, 'Just Like Tom Thumb''s Blues (Cover)', '翻唱自 Bob Dylan <Just Like Tom Thumb''s Blues>。', '2012-08-31 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 5, 'When you''re lost in the rain in Juarez\r\nAnd it''s Eastertime too\r\nAnd your gravity fails\r\nAnd negativity don''t pull you through\r\nDon''t put on any airs\r\nWhen you''re down on Rue Morgue Avenue\r\nThey got some hungry women there \r\nAnd they really make a mess outa you.\r\n\r\nNow if you see Saint Annie\r\nPlease tell her thanks a lot\r\nI cannot move\r\nMy fingers are all in a knot\r\nI don''t have the strength\r\nTo get up and take another shot\r\nAnd my best friend, my doctor\r\nWon''t even say what it is I''ve got.\r\n\r\nSweet Melinda\r\nThe peasants call her the goddess of gloom\r\nShe speaks good English\r\nAnd she invites you up into her room\r\nAnd you''re so kind\r\nAnd careful not to go to her too soon\r\nAnd she takes your voice\r\nAnd leaves you howling at the moon.\r\n\r\nI started out on burgundy\r\nBut soon hit the harder stuff\r\nEverybody said they''d stand behind me\r\nWhen the game got rough\r\nBut the joke was on me\r\nThere was nobody even there to bluff\r\nI''m going back to New York City\r\nI do believe I''ve had enough.\r\n', '', 274, '', 'Bob Dylan', 'Bob Dylan', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-31 15:57:34', '2015-03-12 13:55:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
